{
  "3291130": {
    "name": "QR DEAD",
    "steam_appid": 3291130,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3291130/extras/943e153f5f3e5bf2e49773aceff3b0ee.avif?t=1732729791\" width=620 height=140 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The village seems dead to me. Nobody's around. Only the silly crows keep scaring me... and a pitiful howl pierces the echo of memories every time I walk past the shack. It seems like only my grandfather and I are left.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3291130/extras/785a7ce4ce223af1a2770b9b412a7ce6.poster.avif?t=1732729791\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3291130/extras/785a7ce4ce223af1a2770b9b412a7ce6.webm?t=1732729791\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3291130/extras/785a7ce4ce223af1a2770b9b412a7ce6.mp4?t=1732729791\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >For the past few days, Grandfather hasn't been feeling well. He's been coughing, having trouble breathing, and barely getting out of bed. Today, he asked me to help him in a barely audible voice - to prepare an herbal infusion that, as he said, always got him back on his feet. We didn't have the necessary herbs, so I went to look for them around the village.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3291130/extras/406ec758e5f3474d8663ee1d5b2580cf.poster.avif?t=1732729791\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3291130/extras/406ec758e5f3474d8663ee1d5b2580cf.webm?t=1732729791\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3291130/extras/406ec758e5f3474d8663ee1d5b2580cf.mp4?t=1732729791\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >I went outside... everything seemed strange. A thick fog had descended upon the village, and it was empty. As I walked along the familiar streets, I heard the creaking of old gates and the rustling of leaves, but I didn't meet a single living soul. I started to feel uneasy - the village looked like nobody had lived there for a long time. I returned home, but the silence there was even thicker, even heavier.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3291130/extras/611a118369ab20fc7bac83b76bc2a613.poster.avif?t=1732729791\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3291130/extras/611a118369ab20fc7bac83b76bc2a613.webm?t=1732729791\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3291130/extras/611a118369ab20fc7bac83b76bc2a613.mp4?t=1732729791\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >I tried to pray, like Mom taught me, but the words wouldn't come together in my head.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Instead, I heard a whisper that crept into my mind and drowned out everything else.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It said that my prayers were now meaningless, that prayers wouldn't save me from what had happened here. But what happened? I don't remember...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3291130/extras/748a716236795283d47e909cf83d1cee.poster.avif?t=1732729791\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3291130/extras/748a716236795283d47e909cf83d1cee.webm?t=1732729791\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3291130/extras/748a716236795283d47e909cf83d1cee.mp4?t=1732729791\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >I felt anxious inside... Why can't I calm down?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3291130/extras/a95c7b3963b672335f1807553fbbc84d.poster.avif?t=1732729791\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3291130/extras/a95c7b3963b672335f1807553fbbc84d.webm?t=1732729791\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3291130/extras/a95c7b3963b672335f1807553fbbc84d.mp4?t=1732729791\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3291130/extras/607a9078b424fb8cb379c6f175725a66.avif?t=1732729791\" width=620 height=140 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You'll need a real-life phone to solve the puzzles*. Scan QR codes scattered around the village and look for clues in them. *(Since servers in different countries may be blocked by your government, we added an in-game phone that you can use to scan QR codes and receive hints to complete the game.)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3291130/extras/b6be5985570236974ef697d065a27346.poster.avif?t=1732729791\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3291130/extras/b6be5985570236974ef697d065a27346.webm?t=1732729791\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3291130/extras/b6be5985570236974ef697d065a27346.mp4?t=1732729791\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Escape from the monster in the circle of the holy altar. Find matches by exploring the village and light the candles on the altar to activate the protection.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3291130/extras/7bf9fa20e56f8491fa0c3f559c340773.poster.avif?t=1732729791\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3291130/extras/7bf9fa20e56f8491fa0c3f559c340773.webm?t=1732729791\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3291130/extras/7bf9fa20e56f8491fa0c3f559c340773.mp4?t=1732729791\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3291130/extras/d90f440fe29e8cedb47887c4f222a55e.avif?t=1732729791\" width=620 height=140 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >1. The game has autosave.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >2. Realistic graphics.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >3. High-quality sound design.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >4. Average game completion time: 2 hours.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >5. Genre: Walking Simulator.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3291130/extras/b550997a4b3889d5dbaf7449060c2c67.avif?t=1732729791\" width=620 height=140 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Note! The game features machine translation into the following languages:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- French</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- German</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Spanish</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Portuguese (Brazilian)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Chinese (Simplified)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Korean</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Polish</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Japanese</p>",
